snippet.title: Irony Of Nightmare Announce Trailer
snippet.description:
More information about our game you can find in our groups:
VK - https://vk.com/steppe_hare
Twitter - https://twitter.com/SteppeHare
Facebook - https://www.facebook.com/SteppeHare/
Instagram - https://www.instagram.com/steppeharestudio/

We are supporting youtubers, streamers and other media. If you want to make content about our game, please send us letter with an attached link to your YouTube channel or other source on steppeharestudio@gmail.com. 
You can also leave a request on our Keymailer page: keymailer.co/g/games/52822
